====Usage notes====
* Nouns to which ''abhorrent'' is often applied: behavior, act, crime, practice, thing.
* {{sense|opposed}} ''abhorrent'' is typically folled by ''from''.
* {{sense|contrary}} ''abhorrent'' is followed by ''to''.

